B.a_a=new A.aF(62764,"MaterialIcons",!1)
B.aYS=new A.n5(B.a_a,B.o,"Your Portfolio & Watchlist","You have three lists:\n\n\u2022 Portfolio \u2014 stocks you currently own\n\u2022 Watching \u2014 stocks you're tracking but haven't bought yet\n\u2022 Sold \u2014 your sold stocks and realised gains\n\nTap + on any tab to add a stock to that list.\n\nTap \u21bb in the top right to refresh all prices.")
B.aYR=new A.n5(B.z1,B.dH,"Buy price drives everything","When you add a stock, enter what you paid per share.\n\nThe app uses it to show your profit or loss, your gain in percent, and how much you've made or lost in total.\n\nBought the same stock more than once? Add each purchase separately and the app calculates your average automatically.\n\nWhen you sell, mark it as sold \u2014 your history and realised gains are preserved in the Sold tab.")
B.a_7=new A.aF(62547,"MaterialIcons",!1)
B.aYU=new A.n5(B.a_7,B.o,"Tap any stock to explore","Tapping a stock opens its detail page. Here you'll find:\n\n\u2022 A live price chart\n\u2022 Company info \u2014 P/E ratio, sector, Beta, debt levels\n\u2022 Latest news for that company\n\u2022 Your alert price and target price\n\nThis is your command centre for each stock.")
B.a_q=new A.aF(983823,"MaterialIcons",!1)
B.aYT=new A.n5(B.a_q,B.wF,"Your personal Journal","Every stock has its own journal \u2014 only you can see it.\n\nWrite down why you bought, what your plan is, or how you feel about the position.\n\nIt stays with the stock permanently, so when you look back months later you'll know exactly what you were thinking when you made the decision.\n\nFind it at the bottom of any stock's detail page.")
B.a_j=new A.aF(63548,"MaterialIcons",!0)
B.aYQ=new A.n5(B.a_j,B.a0,"Stay organised with Tags",'Tags let you group stocks into themes \u2014 like "Tech", "Dividend" or "ISA".\n\nA stock can have multiple tags. Add them when you create a stock or from its detail page.\n\nIn the Analysis tab you can filter by tag to see stats for just that group.\n\nHave stocks in different currencies? Set your display currency in Settings and everything converts to one total.')
B.aYO=new A.n5(B.qM,B.a4,"The Analysis tab","The Analysis tab runs the numbers for you \u2014 no setup needed:\n\n\u2022 Equity curve \u2014 a chart of your total value over time\n\u2022 Value at Risk \u2014 how much you could lose on a really bad day\n\u2022 Beta \u2014 whether your portfolio moves more or less than the market\n\u2022 Opportunity cost \u2014 how your watchlist stocks have performed vs what you actually own\n\nFilter by tag at the top to run everything for a specific group.")
B.VN=new A.C(1,0.8509803921568627,0,0.3686274509803922,B.j)
B.aYN=new A.n5(B.kg,B.VN,"Goals & Alerts","Two ways to stay focused:\n\nGoals \u2014 set a target portfolio value and watch your progress build toward it over time. Find it in the Goals tab.\n\nAlert price \u2014 set a price level on any stock. The app flags it the moment the stock crosses that level.\n\nTarget price \u2014 set where you want a stock to be. The app shows how far away it is as a percentage at a glance.")
B.aYP=new A.n5(B.z0,B.dH,"Need a refresher?","The full App Guide is always one tap away.\n\nGo to Settings \u2192 Feature Guide & Glossary to find a searchable reference for every metric, formula, and feature in the app \u2014 from P/E ratio to Value at Risk.\n\nYou can also relaunch this guide any time from the bottom of that screen.")
